modName: TroubleMakers Forsworn Armor - Customizable UNPB and BBP also BBPx
summary:
UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx/UNP-BBP Forsworn Armor / Topless / White Leopard
Standalone and Replacers
descriptionHtml:
This is a mesh conversion/edit of the Forsworn Armor to UNPB BBP. It's based off of calyps conversion to UNPB of abb1 Forsworn topless mod with Rekicker's wonderful Snow Leopard textures.
Working weight slider.

===============================================================================================================================================

Standalone version in main

This is a deconstruct of the armor into its base parts to allow you to wear what you want in the combinations you like.

Items areÂ craftable with elk hide, dear hide, Sabre Cat pelt and Sabre Cat snow pelt. Located in hide section on the Tanning rack, upgradable at the smithing table.
